
This directory will hold the runtime library modules for the native
code implementation of BCPL for the Raspberry Pi.

These libraries and the codegenerator (com/bcplcgrpi.b) were
implemented by D.J.Allerton with minor modifications by M.Richards to
allow them to run under modern Cintcode BCPL. What is planned is both
a cross compiler running on the Cintcode BCPL system and a native code
version of the compiler running directly on the Raspberry Pi.

All this is still under development. Initially this system will be
limited to 32-bit BCPL and will not compile the floating point
operators and constants. But floating point will be available using the
sys(Sys_flt,...) facilities.

MR
